---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <Navbar />

  <main>
    <!-- 主視覺區 -->
    <section class="relative pt-24 pb-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-sky-100 via-white to-slate-50 z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 md:left-20 text-sky-200/60 animate-float"><i data-lucide="cloud" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48"></i></div>
      <div class="absolute top-40 right-10 md:right-32 text-sky-200/60 animate-float-delayed"><i data-lucide="cloud" class="w-20 h-20 md:w-32 md:h-32"></i></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-sky-100 shadow-sm text-sky-600 font-bold mb-8 text-sm md:text-base">
          <i data-lucide="heart-pulse" class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-400"></i>
          <span>蕭宇超醫師的健康冒險島</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">
          告別雲朵身材<br/>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-400 to-blue-600">一起健康生活</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          我是健康冒險島的島主超人醫師蕭宇超，歡迎登島！在這裡我們不只談體重，更是打造讓孩子愛上運動與健康生活的世界。
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="#features" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-amber-400 hover:bg-amber-500 text-slate-900 px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-black text-xl transition-all shadow-lg shadow-amber-200 hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            開始探索互動區
            <i data-lucide="arrow-down-circle" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 互動區 (已經加上 reveal 特效) -->
    <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-white reveal">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-4">探索互動區</h2>
          <div class="w-24 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-300 to-sky-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-sky-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="bg-sky-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500 transition-all duration-300 text-sky-500 group-hover:text-white">
              <i data-lucide="map" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-4">健康冒險島</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
              透過 12 個闖關小遊戲，認識自己的身體，學習健康的飲食技巧、建立運動習慣與放鬆睡眠的秘訣。
            </p>
            <a href="https://smilecloud.tw/for_healthy_children/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl group-hover:bg-sky-50 transition-colors mt-auto">
              立即登島挑戰 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-5 h-5"></i>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-indigo-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="bg-indigo-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-all duration-300 text-indigo-500 group-hover:text-white">
              <i data-lucide="clipboard-check" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-4">身材檢測站</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
              想知道目前的身體是不是雲朵身材嗎？透過簡單的評估，快速了解目前的體位健康狀況。
            </p>
            <a href="https://smilecloud.tw/obesity-survey-app/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-700 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl group-hover:bg-indigo-100 transition-colors mt-auto">
              開始評估檢測 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-5 h-5"></i>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-amber-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="bg-amber-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-amber-500 transition-all duration-300 text-amber-500 group-hover:text-white">
              <i data-lucide="activity" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 mb-4">專屬運動處方</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
              不知道怎麼開始運動？輸入基本資料，立刻為你量身打造專屬的階段性運動計畫。
            </p>
            <a href="https://smilecloud.tw/gogoexercise/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl group-hover:bg-amber-100 transition-colors mt-auto">
              領取專屬處方 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-5 h-5"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>